Hello! I’m the mother of a 

8 year old 4ft 75lbs. White boy in Canada
He was diagnosed at 2.5 years.

We have a  behaviour intervention team ( 2013- present) and he’s on 27-36 mg of concerta (2015- present) 

His academic abilities are very good for his age but his receptive/ expressive language is pretty delayed unless it’s factual.

His anxiety has developed when he began school and remains high with or without stimulant medication.

My BCBA’s & Psychologist are really wanting him on medication for anxiety and we don’t know where to start. 

Any advice is helpful!


Ps

We have been on a wait list for over a year to see a child psychiatrist but we are continuing to wait :( but our team is looking for ideas to bring to the family doctor temporarily 

Thank you in advance
